00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:22.000
[Amit Varma]: Ira Mukherjee, and we'll be talking

00:01:22.000 --> 00:01:24.000
[Amit Varma]: about her book, Daughters of the Sun,

00:01:24.000 --> 00:01:26.000
[Amit Varma]: Empresses, Queens and Begums of the

00:01:26.000 --> 00:01:28.000
[Amit Varma]: Mughal Empire, which was an

00:01:28.000 --> 00:01:30.000
